<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is of utmost importance to us at Peternat PetRegistryApp. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our pet registration application.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>We collect the following information when you register a pet:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Pet's name</li>
    <li>Pet's gender</li>
    <li>Pet's age</li>
    <li>Pet's weight</li>
    <li>Pet's category</li>
    <li>Pet's photo (optional)</li>
</ul>

<p>We do not collect any personally identifiable information about you, the pet owner, other than the information you provide directly related to your pet.</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

<p>The information you provide is used solely for the purpose of maintaining your pet records within the application. We use this information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Display your pet's information in the application.</li>
    <li>Allow you to edit and manage your pet's records.</li>
    <li>Categorize and organize pet information.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Security</h2>

<p>We take appropriate measures to protect your pet's information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. These measures include:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Storing data on secure servers.</li>
    <li>Implementing access controls to restrict unauthorized access.</li>
    <li>Regularly backing up data to prevent data loss.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>

<p>We do not share your pet's information with any third parties, except as required by law or legal process.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>

<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your pet's information at any time.</li>
    <li>Contact us with any questions or concerns about this privacy policy.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated date.</p>

<p>Effective Date: [Date]</p>